ObjectMapper by default will serialize only public fields, but you can change it using ```setVisibility``` [method](https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson-databind/blob/2.14/src/main/java/com/fasterxml/jackson/databind/ObjectMapper.java#L1597).
You can do it like this:
```
TestClass testClass = new TestClass(&quot;field&quot;);
ObjectMapper objectMapper = new ObjectMapper();
objectMapper.setVisibility(PropertyAccessor.FIELD, JsonAutoDetect.Visibility.ANY);
objectMapper.writeValueAsString(testClass);
```

